{
  "stem": "8423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were putting, you know, whatever-- hay, if we go to the barn, we would get some hay and wrap it around our feet--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and put it on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Germany.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then to Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a six week march.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And over 2,000 of us left Christianstadt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And about 400, approximately, a few less, few more, had arrived, actually, in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the rest of them died on the road, either from frost, or starvation, or they simply just gave up, which is what I wanted to do several times.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just pleaded to my sister, let me sit down, and let them shoot me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because whoever couldn't keep up with the march, they would just be shot and left there, left on the road, on the side of the road.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I would say, I'm tired.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just don't want to go any further.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm hungry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm freezing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm sick.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I just want to die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She wouldn't let me die.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She made up all kinds of stories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Tonight, we'll probably find a very nice barn, because that's what they tried to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They tried to-- they walked us on country roads.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they tried to find a barn to put us up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they would take the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They would take the farmer's house, and have hot baths, and so forth, and so on, and a good cooked meal, while we were in the barn.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in the morning, we wouldn't get anything that night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We would arrive there just, you know, absolutely dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But in the morning, the farmers would cook up some potatoes, or turnips, whatever they had.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we would get one or two potatoes, you know, to send us on our way for another day's march.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
